Introduction

This visual data story explores ad exposure based on observational data collected through a structured Google Form. The analysis includes frequency, timing, and sentiment regarding various ad types.

Conclusion

This data story has shown key trends in ad exposure, highlighting which types of ads are most common, when they’re most seen, and how people engage with them. The results offer insight into the user experience of ad saturation in different contexts and times of day.
